'''李德義'''是香港[[恒豐酒店|恒豐酒店]]、[[恒豐中心|恒豐中心]]的主要股東，在香港、東京、倫敦、日內瓦等地擁有近300多個高檔酒店、商鋪、樓宇等物業，根據2017[[福布斯香港富豪榜|福布斯香港富豪榜]]李德義排名第25位。資產達29億美元，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20140109/52074398 |title=【福布斯】地產霸權總身家微跌恒豐李德義新上榜 |access-date=2014-09-30 |archive-date=2017-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415013016/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20140109/52074398 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
但是他最近比較引人注目是兒子[[李建勤|李建勤]]及媳婦[[曾昭穎|曾昭穎]]的離婚案<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20111028/15748520 |title=李德義指兒子全靠他撐腰「我係百億富豪，美金計」 |access-date=2014-09-30 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214543/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20111028/15748520 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/2011-10-21/hongkong1319184908d3493913.html |title=富豪離婚案揭奢華生活 恒豐太子爺李建勤認通姦 |access-date=2014-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006163755/http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/2011-10-21/hongkong1319184908d3493913.html |archive-date=2014-10-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，
媳婦要求五十億多元港元贍養費，但最後法院判媳婦可得12億港元<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20140607/18748260 |title=贍養費減至12億　曾昭穎上訴被拒 |access-date=2014-09-30 |archive-date=2017-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614154727/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20140607/18748260 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

